<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Welcome to the Privacy Policy page of ABC Retail. Your privacy matters to us, and we are dedicated to safeguarding your personal information. This policy outlines how we gather, use, and protect the data you provide when you access our website, utilize our services, or engage with us in any way.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect various types of information to enhance and provide our services. The information we may collect includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Such as your name, email address, contact number, and payment details when you make a purchase or reach out to us.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Data about your interaction with our website and services, like IP address, browser type, and browsing activities.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Details about the device you use to access our site, including device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies and Tracking Technologies:</strong> We utilize cookies and similar technologies to monitor your activities on our website and improve your overall experience.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the collected information for a variety of purposes, such as:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>To Deliver and Enhance Our Services:</strong> Including processing orders, managing accounts, and improving our website’s performance.</li>
    <li><strong>To Communicate with You:</strong> Sending updates, promotional materials, and responding to your queries.</li>
    <li><strong>To Tailor Your Experience:</strong> Providing customized content and recommendations based on your preferences and browsing patterns.</li>
    <li><strong>To Maintain Security:</strong> Protecting our website and services from fraud and ensuring the security of our users.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
<p>We may disclose your information to third parties under the following circumstances:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Sharing data with trusted third-party partners who support us in managing our website and services, such as payment processors and delivery services.</li>
    <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Disclosing information as required by law or in response to legal requests or government inquiries.</li>
    <li><strong>Business Transactions:</strong> Transferring your information as part of a business merger, acquisition, or sale of assets.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Your Choices and Rights</h2>
<p>You have certain rights concerning your personal data:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Access and Update:</strong> You can view and modify your personal information by logging into your account or contacting us.</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> You can choose to stop receiving promotional communications by following the unsubscribe link in our emails.</li>
    <li><strong>Data Deletion:</strong> You may request the deletion of your personal data by contacting us, subject to applicable legal and contractual constraints.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Security</h2>
<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, please note that no method of transmission or electronic storage is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee complete security.</p>

<h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may revise this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any updates will be posted on this page with a new effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we handle your data.</p>

<h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data handling practices, please reach out to us at:</p>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@abcretail.com">support@abcretail.com</a></p>
